Key Insights
Newer vehicle models generated the highest sales revenue.
Revenue is concentrated among a few high-performing vehicle models.
Some vehicle models recorded significantly higher return rates than others.
Customer preferences vary across vehicle categories.
The dashboard enables management to identify profitable products and operational improvement opportunities.
Recommendations
Increase inventory for high-performing vehicle models.
Investigate the causes of frequent vehicle returns.
Reduce inventory for slow-moving vehicles.
Improve customer satisfaction using feedback and ratings.
Continue monitoring sales performance using the Power BI dashboard to support data-driven decision-making
